	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is anything known about the <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_rendering#Cycles_256-319" class="postlink">dummy nametable fetches</a> during sprite pattern fetches?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
